        | B13 MONDAY, AUGUST 3, 2020 THE STRAITS TIMES | | | OBITUARIES Our Deepest Sympathy &
Heartfelt condolence­s to
The Family of our beloved friend and colleague,                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
                                                                                                                                                         JOSEPH TEOH ONG TUCK Age : 83 years                                                                                                             
                                        
                                                 was called home to be with the Lord on 2 August 2020.                                                “For God loved the world so much that He gave his only-begotten Son, so that everyone who believes in Him may not perish but may have eternal life.” John 3:16                                    
                                      
                          
                            
                              
                                                                                                                                                  
                           
                   
                             Dearly missed and fondly remembered by his loved ones. Wife: Vera Sim Bee Guat Son: Stephen Teoh Daughter: Son-in-law: Felicitas Teoh Patrick Teo Sumarto Iskandar                               
                                                                                                        Brothers: Sisters-in-law: Sylvester Teoh (deceased) Tan Puay Eng (deceased) Francis Teoh Thomas Teoh Ng Jin Tuan Departed on 29 July 2020 Sisters: Brothers-in-law: Theresa Teoh Rita Teoh Richard Stanley Tay (deceased) Ng Kah Ting Leong Hon Kong Mery Teoh (deceased) From: and all nephews, nieces, relatives and friends The wake is held at Singapore Casket, Pearl Room, 131 Lavender Street, Singapore 338737, from Sunday 2 Aug 2020, 3.30pm onwards
A Wake service will be held on 4 Aug 2020 at 4.30pm at Church of St Ignatius, 120 King’s Rd, Singapore 268172
Cortège leaves on Tuesday 4 Aug 2020 at 5.00pm for cremation at Mandai Crematoriu­m Hall 3 at 6.00pm. A return Bus service will be provided between Singapore Casket to the Church and Mandai Crematoriu­m. Your DBS Family                                                                                            
                                                                
                                                                   Wake is held at Singapore Casket, 131 Lavender Street, S(338737) Regency Hall, Level 2 until 3 Aug 2020 4pm.      In view of the current situation, we respectful­ly request all those who wish to pay their respects to observe the social distancing measures that will be in place at the wake venue. In addition, the Wake services at Church of St Ignatius & Mandai Crematoriu­m will be limited to immediate family members only.           
              
